        Withdrawing Your Brisbane Property from the Market
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        When to pull a listing, what it actually costs, and how long to wait before relisting. A practical guide for Queensland sellers navigating a campaign that is not going to plan.
      </p>
